maximum capacity

00:43:15.670 --> 00:43:18.320
to take up the opportunity.

00:43:18.320 --> 00:43:20.810
AJAY VIDYASAGAR:
Actually, I think

00:43:20.810 --> 00:43:22.970
I want to share something
